==============================
     ğŸŒ¾ FarmBot Setup
==============================

ğŸ“ Project Structure
frontend/
backend/
env/ (Python virtual environment)

-------------------------------------
1. ACTIVATE PYTHON VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT
-------------------------------------

Windows:
> env\Scripts\activate

-------------------------------------
2. FRONTEND SETUP (TERMINAL 1)
-------------------------------------

> cd frontend
> npm install
> npm run build
> npm run dev

-------------------------------------
3. BACKEND SETUP (TERMINAL 2)
-------------------------------------

> cd backend
> pip install flask flask-socketio speechrecognition deep-translator
> python chat.py

NOTE:
- If you're using NLTK, ensure the 'punkt' tokenizer is downloaded:
    >>> import nltk
    >>> nltk.download('punkt')

-------------------------------------
ğŸ“Œ NOTES:
-------------------------------------

- Ensure both frontend and backend are running in separate terminals.
- The virtual environment ensures package isolation.
- You can deactivate the environment anytime with:
    > deactivate
